 8pt; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; color: #333333; font-family: 新細明體\">各系助教</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; color: #333333; font-family: Verdana\">)</span></td>             </tr>         </tbody>     </table>     <br />      </li> </ul>','碩士班98學年度第1學期辦理論文口試相關時程','','publish','open','open','','981-sp-2283','','','2009-06-17 16:00:00','2009-06-17 08:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=213',103,'post','',0);
