: 14pt\">名額</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 189pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"252\">             <div><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">名</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">專兼任</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">兼任教師</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">任教科目</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">行動資訊系統</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">學歷及資格</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一、須具國內外碩士學位</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">含</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">以上為原則；持國外學歷者應經駐外單位完成認證程序。</span></div>             <div style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二、具講師級之教師資格證書且與任教科目相關教學或專業工作經驗者。</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">應徵手續</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><br />             </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">及日期</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一、申請日期：自即日起至本（</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">100</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">）年</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">28</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">日</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">星期一</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">止（郵戳為憑）。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; text-indent: -31.5pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 31.5pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二、檢附資料：</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 3.6pt 0pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">（一）填寫本系兼任教師申請表（請上本系網站下載）。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -55.7pt; margin: 0cm 3.6pt 0pt 55.7pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">  </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">（二）檢附<b><u>最高學歷證書影本</u></b>、<b><u>現在職證明影本</u></b>及<b><u>經歷聘書影本</u></b>、<b><u>教師資格證書影本</u></b>、<b><u>簡要自述</u></b>、<b><u>近</u></b></span><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">5</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">年內與應聘科目有關之著作目錄</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">、<b><u>任教科目教學計畫（含期末考共</u></b></span><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">18</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">週）</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">缺一不可</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; text-indent: -27pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 27pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">    </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">前述資料，請備妥乙份並裝訂成乙冊，以掛號郵寄或親送至「</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">106</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">台北市大安區和平東路</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">段</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">134</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">號，國立臺北教育大學數位科技設計學系含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班收」。逾期恕不受理，重要資料請繳交影本。聯絡人及電話：（</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">02</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">2732-1104</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">轉</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">2478 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">許文怡助教。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -28.05pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 28.05pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">★請於信封上註明所應徵科目；例，行動資訊系統兼任教師。</span></b></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">三、應徵者於甄選結束後若需寄回應徵資料，請附貼足郵資之回郵信封。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">四、待遇：依本校兼任教師相關規定核支。</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"height: 20pt\">             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 20pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">網址</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 20pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph\"><u><span style=\"color: blue\">http://dtd.ntue.edu.tw</span></u></div>             </td>         </tr>     </tbody> </table>','數位系徵100學年度第二學期大學部「行動資訊系統」兼任教師','','publish','open','open','','100-sp-392','','','2011-11-22 03:11:54','2011-11-21 19:11:54','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=393',74,'post','',0);
