0cm\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">設計心理學</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">學歷及資格</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一、須具國內外碩士學位</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">含</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">以上為原則；持國外學歷者應經駐外單位完成認證程序。</span></div>             <div style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二、具講師級之教師資格證書且與任教科目相關教學或專業工作經驗者。</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">應徵手續</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"><br />             </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">及日期</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" valign=\"top\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一、申請日期：自即日起至本（</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">100</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">）年</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">日</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">星期五</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">止（郵戳為憑）。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; text-indent: -31.5pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 31.5pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二、檢附資料：</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; margin: 0cm 3.6pt 0pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">（一）填寫本系兼任教師申請表（請上本系網站下載</span><u><span style=\"color: blue\">http://dtd.ntue.edu.tw</span></u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">）。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -55.7pt; margin: 0cm 3.6pt 0pt 55.7pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">（二）檢附<b><u>最高學歷證書影本</u></b>、<b><u>現在職證明影本</u></b>及<b><u>經歷聘書影本</u></b>、<b><u>教師資格證書影本</u></b>、<b><u>簡要自述</u></b>、<b><u>近</u></b></span><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">5</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">年內與應聘科目有關之著作目錄</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">、<b><u>任教科目教學計畫（含期末考共</u></b></span><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">18</span></u></b><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">週）</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">缺一不可</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; text-indent: -27pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 27pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">    </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">前述資料，請備妥乙份並裝訂成乙冊，以掛號郵寄或親送至「</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">106</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">台北市大安區和平東路</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">段</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">134</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">號，國立臺北教育大學數位科技設計學系含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班收」。逾期恕不受理，重要資料請繳交影本。聯絡人及電話：（</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">02</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">2732-1104</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">轉</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">2478 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">許文怡助教。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -28.05pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 28.05pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">★請於信封上註明所應徵科目；例，設計心理學兼任教師。</span></b></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 16pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 28pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">三、應徵者於甄選結束後若需寄回應徵資料，請附貼足郵資之回郵信封。</span></div>             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; margin: 6pt 3.6pt 0pt 0cm; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">四、待遇：依本校兼任教師相關規定核支。</span></div>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"height: 20pt\">             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 90pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 20pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"120\">             <div align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">網址</span></b></div>             </td>             <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 450pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 20pt; border-top: #f0f0f0; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\" width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\">             <div style=\"text-justify: inter-ideograph\"><u><span style=\"color: blue\">http://dtd.ntue.edu.tw</span></u></div>             </td>         </tr>     </tbody> </table>','數位系徵100學年度第二學期大學部「設計心理學」兼任教師','','publish','open','open','','100-sp-29444','','','2011-11-25 01:54:01','2011-11-24 17:54:01','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=394',73,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (599,1,'2011-12-05 03:30:47','2011-12-04 19:30:47','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">蕭瑛東主任及俞齊山老師指導本系(含玩遊碩士班)及資訊科學系(含碩士班)學生吳昱霆、周湘寧、林廷達、韓秉軒、施登文、王韻涵參加2011臺北數位創作競賽，以作品「台北憶世界」榮獲佳作!!<br /> <br /> 數位系(含玩遊碩班)全體師生敬賀</span></p>','【狂賀】本系(含玩遊碩士班)與資科系學生參加2011臺北數位創作競賽榮獲佳作','','publish','open','open','','2011-sp-20687','','','2011-12-05 03:30:47','2011-12-04 19:30:47','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=395',55,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (600,1,'2011-12-06 06:19:52','2011-12-05 22:19:52','<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">本系巴白山教授指導玩遊碩士班學生廖婉詞、黃聖元參加中華產業創新競爭力協會舉辦100年度「奈米科技創意產品設計競賽」，以作品「無設線」、「Color  umbrella」、「Spore。Light」榮獲優勝!!<br /> <br /> 數位系(含玩遊碩班)全體師生敬賀</span></p>','【狂賀】本系玩遊碩士班學生參加100年度「奈米科技創意產品設計競賽」榮獲優勝','','publish','open','open','','100-4','','','2011-12-06 06:19:52','2011-12-05 22:19:52','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=396',54,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (601,1,'2011-12-09 04:41:02','2011-12-08 20:41:02','本系巴白山老師、楊孟哲老師指導玩遊碩士班學生張威彥、孫齊蔚、羅雅宣、鄭偉志參加100學年度台灣區電腦化運動競技大賽─機器人專題競賽，以作品「TOY智慧型手杖」榮獲佳作!!<br /> <br /> 本系(含玩遊碩班)全體師生敬賀','【狂賀】本系玩遊碩士班學生參加100學年度台灣區電腦化運動競技大賽榮獲佳作','','publish','open','open','','100-sp-9040','','','2011-12-09 04:41:02','2011-12-08 20:41:02','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=397',53,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (602,1,'2011-12-14 02:18:45','2011-12-13 18:18:45','<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">狂賀本系玩遊碩士班學生參加經濟部工業局所主辦總獎金高達140萬的 2011 APP STAR 高手爭霸戰，勇奪學生組第一名與第三名，王學武教授並獲得大會最佳指導老師獎。</span></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"> </span></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">APP 是政府目前內容產業的重點發展方向，經濟部工業局特別在2011年首次舉辦 APP STAR 高手爭霸戰，總獎金則高達 140萬。學生組部分共吸引來自台、清、交等全國共 100 多組的參賽隊伍，本系玩遊碩士班學生王漢偉、邱奕撰以作品「Constant C」獲得學生組第一名，指導老師為范丙林教授。學生陳宜均、蔡佳穎、黃筱崴則以作品「玩具實驗室」獲得學生組第三名，指導老師為王學武教授。王學武教授並同時獲得大會最佳指導老師獎。</span></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"> </span></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">數位系(含玩遊碩班)全體師生敬賀</span></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"> </span></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">相關連結：</span></div> <div><a href=\"http://www.jtv.com.tw/AppStar/show.php?no=22\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">http://www.jtv.com.tw/AppStar/show.php?no=22</font></span></a></div> <div><a href=\"http://www.ttv.com.tw/Taiwan/TTVInfo/TTVInfo3300.htm\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><font color=\"#0000ff\">http://www.ttv.com.tw/Taiwan/TTVInfo/TTVInfo3300.htm</font></span></a><br />  </div>','【狂賀】本系玩遊碩士班學生參加2011 APP STAR高手爭霸戰，勇奪學生組第一名與第三名，王學武教授並獲得大會最佳指導老師獎','','publish','open','open','','2011-app-star','','','2011-12-14 02:18:45','2011-12-13 18:18:45','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=398',52,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (603,1,'2011-12-28 01:02:02','2011-12-27 17:02:02','數位科技設計學系100學年度第一學期期末專題展已於100年12月27日圓滿結束<br /> 人氣獎投票8G隨身碟已於會後由本系王學武老師抽出共十位幸運的獲獎同學<br /> 以下同學請於100年1月13日(星期五)前到系辦領取獎品，謝謝!!<br /> <br /> <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"175\">     <colgroup><col width=\"103\" style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:3296;width:77pt\">  <col width=\"72\" style=\"width:54pt\">  </colgroup>     <tbody>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td width=\"103\" height=\"32\" style=\"height: 24pt; width: 77pt; text-align: left;\" class=\"xl66\">數位一甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl67\">金孟璇</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt\" class=\"xl66\">數位一甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl68\">劉尚</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt\" class=\"xl65\">數位一甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl68\">陳威郡</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt\" class=\"xl71\">數位一甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl69\">張紘銘</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt;border-top:none\" class=\"xl65\">數位二甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl68\">蔡為恩</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt;border-top:none\" class=\"xl65\">數位三甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl68\">陳代祐</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt;border-top:none\" class=\"xl65\">數位四甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl70\">康學昕</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt;border-top:none\" class=\"xl65\">數位四甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl68\">鄭尹惠</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt;border-top:none\" class=\"xl65\">數位四甲</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-top:none;border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl68\">蔡華棣</td>         </tr>         <tr height=\"32\" style=\"mso-height-source:userset;height:24.0pt\">             <td height=\"32\" style=\"height:24.0pt\" class=\"xl71\">玩遊碩一</td>             <td width=\"72\" style=\"border-left:none;width:54pt\" class=\"xl69\">郭澔</td>         </tr>     </tbody> </table> <br />','數位科技設計學系100學年度第一學期期末專題展人氣獎投票8G隨身碟獲獎名單','','publish','open','open','','1008g','','','2011-12-28 01:02:02','2011-12-27 17:02:02','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=400',72,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (604,1,'2011-12-28 08:20:01','2011-12-28 00:20:01','<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:\">學年度第一學期期末專題成果於</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span style=\"font-family:\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日圓滿結束</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">!!</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">經由參觀觀眾投票選出人氣最高前三名以及由本系老師評分後選出大學部及碩士班前三名，各頒發獎金，以鼓勵同學們的優秀創作。</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">得獎名單如下：</span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">人氣票選獎</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">共三組，每組獎金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:\">元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:\">大學部</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>ROLLING(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">黃御恩、張廷宇、王昶中、康學昕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:\">大學部</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>3D</span><span style=\"font-family:\">格鬥遊戲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:\">校園計畫一號</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">蔡華棣、鄭尹惠、林劭儒、愓惟馨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:\">碩士班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>Effect Man(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">韓秉軒、張銀軒、簡鈺軒、張凱鈞</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">大學部</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">獎金第一名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:\">元，第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:\">名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:\">元，第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:\">名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:\">元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">第一名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>Sky High(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">隋佳蓉、蔡佩均</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">第二名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:\">箱子地獄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">簡志宇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">第三名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>ROLLING(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">黃御恩、張廷宇、王昶中、康學昕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">碩士班</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">獎金第一名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span style=\"font-family:\">元，第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:\">名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:\">元，第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:\">名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family:\">元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">第一名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>Constant C(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">王漢偉、邱亦撰</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family:\">第二名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:\">玩具實驗室</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:\">黃筱葳、陳宜均、蔡佳穎</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)<br /> </span></p> <p style=\"line-height:10.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\">第三名 鋼鐵擂台<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>蕭文祥、高錫研、唐偉豪、邱亦撰<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></p> 第三名  Effect Man(韓秉軒、張銀軒、簡鈺軒、張凱鈞) <p><span new=\"New\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"> </span></p>','數位科技設計學系(含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班)100學年度第一學期期末專題成果得獎名單','','publish','open','open','','100-sp-2812','','','2011-12-28 08:20:01','2011-12-28 00:20:01','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=401',71,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (605,1,'2011-12-30 03:59:57','2011-12-29 19:59:57','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">本系大學部學生壽士壯、金克杰、張紘銘參加龍華科技大學多媒體與遊戲發展科學系舉辦之「24小時遊戲原型創作競賽」，以作品「The Tail」榮獲優勝!!<br /> <br /> 數位系/玩遊碩班全體師生敬賀</span></p>','【狂賀】本系大學部學生參加24小時遊戲原型創作競賽榮獲優勝','','publish','open','open','','24-2','','','2011-12-30 03:59:57','2011-12-29 19:59:57','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=402',51,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (606,1,'2012-01-05 06:26:00','2012-01-04 22:26:00','【狂賀】本系數位三甲游茜微、陳貞元、董君慧、徐珮宜、徐紹銘、謝宏安參加2011哈客遊戲設計比賽，作品「桐遊客家庄」榮獲季軍。 指導老師：范丙林老師。','【狂賀】本系數位三甲游茜微、陳貞元、董君慧、徐珮宜、徐紹銘、謝宏安參加2011哈客遊戲設計比賽，作品「桐遊客家庄」榮獲季軍。','','publish','open','open','','2011-4','','','2012-01-05 06:26:00','2012-01-04 22:26:00','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=403',50,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (607,1,'2012-01-05 09:02:36','2012-01-05 01:02:36','狂賀本系玩遊碩士班學生王漢偉、邱亦撰由范丙林老師指導之作品「Constant C」參加遠傳S市集 APP星光大賞 勇奪「年度最佳遊戲」、「最佳創意」、及「校園新秀」三項大獎，總獎金高達53萬元。本作品繼獲得經濟部工業局所主辦2011 APP STAR 高手爭霸戰學生組第一名後，再次受到肯定！！！\n\n\n數位系(含玩遊碩班)全體師生敬賀','【狂賀】本系學生作品「Constant C」勇奪「年度最佳遊戲」、「最佳創意」、及「校園新秀」三項大獎。','','publish','open','open','','constant-cs-app','','','2012-01-05 09:02:36','2012-01-05 01:02:36','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=404',49,'post','',0);
