an style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">系所</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"520\" style=\"width:389.85pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:            solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:34.0pt\" colspan=\"3\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:-.2pt;mso-para-margin-left:            -.04gd;text-align:center;text-indent:-.3pt;mso-char-indent-count:-.02\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">數位科技設計系含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班</span></b></p>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:35.15pt\">             <td width=\"142\" style=\"width:106.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:            none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:35.15pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">職位</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"306\" style=\"width:229.55pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;            border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:35.15pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">助理教授級</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體\">(</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">含</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:            標楷體\">)</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">以上</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"64\" style=\"width:48.0pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:            solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-top-alt:            solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:            solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:35.15pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">名額</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"150\" style=\"width:112.3pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;            border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:35.15pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體\">1</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">名</span></b></p>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:2;height:63.3pt\">             <td width=\"142\" style=\"width:106.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:            none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:63.3pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">學歷及資格</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"520\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:389.85pt;border-top:none;            border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:63.3pt\" colspan=\"3\">             <p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">具國內外大學博士學位為<span style=\"color: red;\">原則</span>，持國外學歷者，畢業證書及成績單應經駐外單位完成驗證，並附中文譯本。</span></span></p>             <p style=\"text-indent:.1pt;tab-stops:-242.4pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">具備美術與視覺設計的專業背景、<span lang=\"EN-US\">2D/3D </span>動畫、數位遊戲設計有實際製作經驗、並有個人參賽或指導學生參賽得獎者、敬業樂群且善於指導專題學生、有教學經驗者優先考量。</span></span></p>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:3;height:49.8pt\">             <td width=\"142\" style=\"width:106.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:            none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:49.8pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">專長</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"520\" style=\"width:389.85pt;border-top:none;border-left:            none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:49.8pt\" colspan=\"3\">             <p style=\"tab-stops:42.55pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">視覺傳達與設計、<span lang=\"EN-US\">2D</span>繪圖<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>包含手繪、電繪<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>與<span lang=\"EN-US\">2D/3D</span>電腦動畫、數位遊戲設計</span></b></p>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:4;height:53.25pt\">             <td width=\"142\" style=\"width:106.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:            none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:53.25pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">應聘科目</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"520\" style=\"width:389.85pt;border-top:none;border-left:            none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt;height:53.25pt\" colspan=\"3\">             <p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;            font-family:標楷體\">角色造型設計</span></b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;            font-family:標楷體\">、<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2D </span>動畫實務、電腦動畫、電腦繪圖、中外奇幻文學、多媒體美工與音效實務</b></span></p>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:5\">             <td width=\"142\" style=\"width:106.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:            none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">應徵手續及日期</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"520\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:389.85pt;border-top:none;            border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt\" colspan=\"3\">             <p style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">一、應徵手續</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:12.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.0gd;            mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">一<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>填寫本系專任教師申請表</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:31.3pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.0gd;            text-indent:-19.3pt;mso-char-indent-count:-1.61;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">二<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>檢附下列證明與資料：</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">最高學位<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>學歷<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>畢業證書影本</span></span></p>             <ul>                 <li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">持國外學歷者，畢業證書及成績單應經駐外單位完成驗證</span></span></li>             </ul>             <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:12.7pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:67.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:1.06gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            67.3pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>             <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">             <ul>                 <li><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">已通過博士學位論文口試者，請出具學位口試通過證明<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>須於<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: red;\">101</span><span style=\"color: red;\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>日</span>前取得博士畢業證書<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></li>             </ul>             </span>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">博碩士成績單</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">個人簡歷</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>             <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">著作目錄<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含展演與作品集<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>、博士論文<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>近<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>年畢業者<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>、近<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>年代表著作<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>論文發表或展演、作品<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></p>             </span>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>             <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">在職證明<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>無在職者，可免附本項資料<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></p>             </span>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>             <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">教師證書影本<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>非教師者，可免附本項資料<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></p>             </span>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">7.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">重要經歷<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>工作<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>證明</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">8.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">國民身份證正反面影本</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:43.3pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">9.</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">其他有利於審查之相關資料。</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-left:31.3pt;mso-para-margin-left:1.0gd;            text-indent:-19.3pt;mso-char-indent-count:-1.61;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">三<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>請就應聘主要科目「角色造型設計」、「<span lang=\"EN-US\">2D</span>動畫實務」、「電腦動畫<span lang=\"EN-US\">(3D)</span>」、「電腦繪圖」、「中外奇幻文學」與「多媒體美工與音效實務」檢附教學大綱<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (</span>含期末考共<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>週<span lang=\"EN-US\">)1</span>份，並於<span style=\"color: red;\">「角色造型設計」、「<span lang=\"EN-US\">2D</span>動畫實務」和「電腦動畫<span lang=\"EN-US\">(3D)</span>」三科目，</span>撰寫教學計畫<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含<span style=\"color: red;\">部分單元講義</span>及輔助教學資源<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，共<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>份<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>本項目內容可以紙本或光碟繳交<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:19.8pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:31.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:1.65gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            1.0gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-19.3pt;mso-char-indent-count:            -1.61;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>             <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">             <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:19.8pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:31.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:1.65gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            1.0gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-19.3pt;mso-char-indent-count:            -1.61;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">四<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>以上文件請掛號郵寄至：『<span lang=\"EN-US\">10671</span>台北市和平東路<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>段<span lang=\"EN-US\">134</span>號 國立臺北教育大學數位科技設計系<span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span>許文怡助教收』。<span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></span></p>             </span>             <p style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;mso-pagination:            widow-orphan;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 42.0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>             <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">             <ul>                 <li><b><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">請於信封上註明：應徵專任教師   </span></b></li>             </ul>             </span>             <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:5.65pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:23.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:.47gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            23.9pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-23.9pt;mso-char-indent-count:            -1.99;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">二、送件日期：自即日起至<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: red;\">101</span><span style=\"color: red;\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span>日止</span>，以郵戳為憑，欲應徵者請儘早郵寄<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>恕不接受親送，請見諒！<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。</span></span></p>             <p style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">三、應徵者於甄選結束若需寄回應徵資料，請附貼足郵票之回郵信封。</span></span></p>             <p style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">四、待遇：待遇依本校相關規定核支。</span></span></p>             <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:5.65pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:23.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:.47gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            23.9pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-23.9pt;mso-char-indent-count:            -1.99;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>             <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">             <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:5.65pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:23.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:.47gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            23.9pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-23.9pt;mso-char-indent-count:            -1.99;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體; color: red;\">五、起聘學年度：<span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span>學年度第二學期。</span></u></b></p>             </span>             <p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:5.65pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:23.9pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:.47gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            23.9pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-23.9pt;mso-char-indent-count:            -1.99;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 標楷體;\">六、如有相關問題請洽許助教。聯絡電話<span lang=\"EN-US\">:(02)27321104</span>分機<span lang=\"EN-US\">62478</span></span></span></p>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:6;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes\">             <td width=\"142\" style=\"width:106.45pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:            none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt\">             <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:\" new=\"New\">網址</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"520\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:389.85pt;border-top:none;            border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 1.4pt 0cm 1.4pt\" colspan=\"3\">             <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:            標楷體\">http://dtd.ntue.edu.tw/</span></p>             </td>         </tr>     </tbody> </table> </div> <p style=\"margin-right:48.0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:標楷體\"> </span></b></p>','國立臺北教育大學101學年度第1學期新聘專任教師甄選公告','','publish','open','open','','1011-2','','','2012-09-21 04:12:35','2012-09-20 20:12:35','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=520',41,'post','',0);
