top:.5gd;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            31.5pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            text-indent:-31.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:-2.25;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;            layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;            mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:            Arial\">二、檢附資料：</span></p>             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:3.6pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:31.5pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:.5gd;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            31.5pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            text-indent:-31.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:-2.25;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;            layout-grid-mode:char\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            \"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span>(</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;            mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">填寫本系兼任教師申請表（請上本系網站下載</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">http://dtd.ntue.edu.tw</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">）。</span></p>             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:3.6pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:55.7pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            55.7pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            text-indent:-55.7pt;mso-char-indent-count:-3.98;line-height:16.0pt;            mso-line-height-rule:exactly;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"font-size:            14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:            Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">（二）檢附<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u>最高學歷證書影本</u></b>、<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u>現在職證明影本</u></b>及<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><u>經歷聘書影本</u></b>、<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u>教師資格證書影本</u></b>、<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u>簡要自述</u></b>、<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><u>近</u></b></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">5</span></u></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:            Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">年內與應聘科目有關之著作目錄</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">、<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><u>任教科目教學計畫（含期末考共</u></b></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">18</span></u></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:            Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">週）</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;            mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">缺一不可</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:            14.0pt;font-family:\">)</span></p>             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:3.6pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:55.7pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:0cm;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            55.7pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            text-indent:-55.7pt;mso-char-indent-count:-3.98;line-height:16.0pt;            mso-line-height-rule:exactly;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">   </span>(</span><span style=\"font-size:            14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:            Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">三</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:            14.0pt;font-family:\">) </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">應徵「虛擬實境」兼任教師者，請以<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><u>「</u></b></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">unity3D</span></u></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:            Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">」為教學工具撰寫教學計畫</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">。</span></p>             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:3.6pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:27.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:.5gd;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            27.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            text-indent:-27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-1.93;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;            layout-grid-mode:char\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            \"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">    </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;            mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">前述資料，請備妥乙份並裝訂成乙冊，以掛號郵寄至「</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">106</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:            Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">台北市大安區和平東路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;            mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">段</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:\">134</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">號，國立臺北教育大學數位科技設計學系含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班收」。逾期恕不受理，重要資料請繳交影本。聯絡人及電話：（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">02</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;            mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:\">2732-1104</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;            mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">轉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\">62478 </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;            font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;            mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">許文怡助教。</span></p>             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:3.6pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:28.05pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:.5gd;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            28.05pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            text-indent:-28.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:-2.0;line-height:16.0pt;            mso-line-height-rule:exactly;layout-grid-mode:char\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:            normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:            Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">★請於信封上註明所應徵科目；例，應徵「虛擬實境」兼任教師。</span></b></p>             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:3.6pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:28.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:.5gd;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            28.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            text-indent:-28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:-2.0;line-height:16.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:            exactly;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:            Arial\">三、應徵者於甄選結束後若需寄回應徵資料，請附貼足郵資之回郵信封。</span></p>             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:3.6pt;margin-bottom:            0cm;margin-left:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-para-margin-top:.5gd;            mso-para-margin-right:.3gd;mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;mso-para-margin-left:            0cm;mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;            layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;            mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:            Arial\">四、待遇：依本校兼任教師相關規定核支。</span></p>             </td>         </tr>         <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:5;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;height:20.0pt\">             <td width=\"120\" style=\"width:90.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:            none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:20.0pt\">             <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:            標楷體;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:            Arial\">網址</span></b></p>             </td>             <td width=\"600\" colspan=\"3\" style=\"width:450.0pt;border-top:none;border-left:            none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;            mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;            mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:20.0pt\">             <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"><a href=\"http://dtd.ntue.edu.tw\">http://dtd.ntue.edu.tw</a></span></u></p>             </td>         </tr>     </tbody> </table>','數位系徵101學年度第二學期大三選修「虛擬實境」兼任教師','','publish','open','open','','101-sp-24107','','','2012-11-21 06:28:29','2012-11-20 22:28:29','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=582',63,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (683,1,'2012-11-22 03:26:35','2012-11-21 19:26:35','<div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"color: black\">恭賀</span></span></span></div> <div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"color: black\">資科系蕭瑛東主任蟬聯</span></span></span></div> <div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"color: black\">中華民國民生電子學會第三屆理事</span></span></span></div> <div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"> </span></span></div> <div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"color: black\">數位科技設計學系</span></span></span></div> <div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"color: black\">資訊科學系</span></span></span></div> <div><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"color: black\">全體師生  同賀</span></span></span></div>','【狂賀】蕭瑛東老師蟬聯中華民國民生電子學會第三屆理事','','publish','open','open','','2012-11-22-03-40-52','','','2012-11-22 03:26:35','2012-11-21 19:26:35','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=583',36,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (684,1,'2012-11-22 05:02:25','2012-11-21 21:02:25','<p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><br /> 一、<b>報到時間：<strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">101</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">年</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">24</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt\">日（星期六）</span></strong>上午8時50分起，<u>至遲須於口試叫號前完成報到手續</u></b>。</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">二、報到地點：本校科學館5樓507室。</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><b>三、應繳驗證件資料：</b></span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><b>（一）繳驗<u>國民身分證</u>及<u>第一階段錄取通知函</u>（均需正本）。</b></span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><b>（二）繳驗<u>第2階段口試費用繳款收據或ATM交易明細表</u>。</b></span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">四、報到流程：</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"> （一）請於報到時間內至本校科學館5樓報到，<b>逾時不受理報到，未辦理報到者視同放棄口試資格。</b></span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"> （二）完成報到手續後，請依現場服務人員指示至休息區等候。</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"> （三）口試於上午9:00起進行，口試完成後始得離開口試試場。</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">五、攜帶電子通訊用品（含行動電話、呼叫器或具通訊功能之任何電子用品），請務必關機。<br /> 六、其他注意事項：</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">（一）<b><u>口試順序經公告後不予調整。</u></b></span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">（二）請於口試前30分鐘提早至考場等候，<b><u>口試前叫號三次未到者，視同放棄口試資格</u></b>。口試時間為10分鐘（含3分鐘器材設置準備），於第9分鐘時響鈴1短聲；於10分鐘時響鈴3短聲，以提醒考生口試時間已到，請立即離開口試場地。</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">（三）為不影響其他考生之權益，禁止在考場範圍內隨意走動，並請於口試完畢後依照現場服務人員指示立即離開試場，切勿返回休息區等待。</span></span></p> <p><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">七、<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00\">考生休息室內禁止飲食</span>。</span></span></p>','102學年度玩具與遊戲設計碩士班推甄第2階段口試時間表','','publish','open','open','','1022-2','','','2012-11-22 05:02:25','2012-11-21 21:02:25','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=584',35,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (685,1,'2012-11-22 07:43:00','2012-11-21 23:43:00','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\">數位科技設計學系<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班<span lang=\"EN-US\">)101</span>學年度第一學期期末專題成果展</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"> </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\">謹訂於<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>星期二<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>上午九點至下午四點舉行</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:\"> </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\">展演地點於本校篤行樓一樓川堂</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\">現場有本系大學部及碩士班之展出作品，更有多項榮獲大獎之作品，千萬不可錯過！</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\">本次期末專題展將依據每位老師的評分，於大四學生及碩士班的作品中，各選出前三名頒發獎金以茲鼓勵，</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background:silver;mso-highlight:silver\"> </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\">敬請老師能蒞臨為辛苦認真的學生們，指導參觀並協助評分，讓優秀的作品有獲獎的機會。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:\">現場觀眾，可至服務台領取選票，票選心目中的最佳人氣作品，展出後，將從投票箱中抽出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:\">位幸運參觀者，每位可得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:red\">8 G</span><span style=\"font-family:\">隨身碟一隻。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\">大學部三年級分組進度報告，時間訂於同天<span lang=\"EN-US\">12/18(</span>星期二<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>下午二點，簡報地點於篤行樓<span lang=\"EN-US\">Y406</span>，敬請老師到場為各位學生評分及指導。</span>','101學年度第一學期期末專題成果展於12/18展出','','publish','open','open','','1011218-2','','','2012-11-22 07:43:00','2012-11-21 23:43:00','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=585',34,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (688,1,'2012-12-03 09:18:09','2012-12-03 01:18:09','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">本系范丙林教授指導學生林昂東、鄧暉參加2012-4C數位創作競賽-遊戲創作組-PC，以作品「牠們來了」榮獲大會銀獎與樂陞贊助獎!!<br /> <br /> 數位系/玩遊碩班 全體師生 敬賀</span></p>','【狂賀】本系大學部學生參加2012-4C數位創作競賽榮獲大會銀獎與樂陞贊助獎','','publish','open','open','','2012-4c','','','2012-12-03 09:18:09','2012-12-03 01:18:09','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=588',35,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (689,1,'2012-12-04 09:40:27','2012-12-04 01:40:27','<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">本系玩遊碩士班學生參加第四屆本土生命繪本暨動畫創作徵選活動，榮獲繪本類佳作!!<br /> 指導老師：巴白山老師、盧姝如老師、楊孟哲老師<br /> 參賽學生：吳佳璋、黎俞均、林玫均<br /> 作品名稱：說給史豔文聽<br /> <br /> 數位系/玩遊碩士班 全體師生 敬賀</span>','【狂賀】本系玩遊碩士班學生參加第四屆本土生命繪本暨動畫創作徵選活動榮獲繪本類佳作','','publish','open','open','','2012-12-04-09-53-57','','','2012-12-04 09:40:27','2012-12-04 01:40:27','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=589',34,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (690,1,'2012-12-04 09:54:21','2012-12-04 01:54:21','<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">本系玩遊碩士班學生參加2012漢字動畫創意競賽，榮獲最佳故事片獎!!<br /> 指導老師：巴白山教授<br /> 參賽學生：李育馨、林育嬋、林玫均、廖婉詞、趙詠捷、黎俞均<br /> 作品名稱：箏心話<br /> <br /> 數位系/玩遊碩士班 全體師生 敬賀</span>','【狂賀】本系玩遊碩士班學生參加2012漢字動畫創意競賽榮獲最佳故事片獎','','publish','open','open','','2012-sp-25995','','','2012-12-04 09:54:21','2012-12-04 01:54:21','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=590',33,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (691,1,'2012-12-05 07:51:34','2012-12-04 23:51:34','<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 125%; layout-grid-mode: char\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 125%; font-size: 18pt\">國立臺北教育大學教務處教學發展中心　公告</span></div> <div style=\"text-align: right; line-height: 125%; layout-grid-mode: char\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"line-height: 125%; font-size: 14pt\">101</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; font-size: 14pt\">年</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; font-size: 14pt\">12</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; font-size: 14pt\">月</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; font-size: 14pt\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; font-size: 14pt\">日</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -42pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">主旨：公告本校</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">101</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">學年度第</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">學期學生申請停修課程相關事宜。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -42pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">依據：本校學生申請停修課程實施要點</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">如附件一</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">公告事項：</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 40pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一、申請停修作業：</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -25.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 70.65pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">申請原因：</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">於加退選課程截止後，因所修讀課程內容不符興趣，或因特殊情形致部分課程失去修讀動機。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -7pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 51.9pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">申請期限：</span><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">101</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">年</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">12</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">月</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">10</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">日</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">(</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">星期一</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">)</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">至</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">12</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">月</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">21</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">日</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">(</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">星期五</span></u><u><span style=\"background: #d9d9d9; font-size: 14pt\">)</span></u></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -67.2pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 69.95pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">      (</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">三</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">申請文件：停修課程申請表</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">如附表</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">1)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">，並請檢附本學期選課資料</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">可自行至「學生資訊系統」、「線上查詢」、「歷年成績查詢」列印系統頁面</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -66.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 69.15pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">      (</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">四</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">申請流程：學生申請停修課程，應填妥停修課程申請表，經任課教師及系（所）主管之同意，日間學制學生於<u>停修作業申請期限內</u>將停修申請表送交教務處教學發展中心辦理。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 40pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二、</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">各學制停修課程數及學分數限制</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">：</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -25.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 70.05pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">學士班：</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">每學期停修學分數以該年級最低應修學分數三分之一（四捨五入）為限，且不得低於該年級最低修習學分數。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -28.55pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 73.45pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> (1)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">大一至大三：可申請停修學分上限為5學分，扣除停修之學分數後，不得少於16學分。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -29.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 74.25pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> (2)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">大四：停修上限3學分，扣除停修之學分數後，不得少於10學分</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -7pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 51.9pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> (3)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">延長修業年限學生：扣除停修課程學分後至少應修習一門科目。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -25.05pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 70.05pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">日間學制碩博士班</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">：</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">扣除停修科目之學分數後，應符合各系、所最低應修學分數之規定。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">三、注意事項：</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -70pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 70pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">      (</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">一</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">停修課程仍須登記於該學期成績單及歷年成績表，於成績欄註明「停修」。停修課程之學分數不計入該學期修習學分總數。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">      (</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">二) 註冊繳交之費用不予退費，未繳交者應補繳後方得提出申請。</span></div> <div style=\"line-height: 22pt; text-indent: -76.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 76.3pt; layout-grid-mode: char\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">      (</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">三)</span> <span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">應屆畢業生申請停修課程請自行確認是否已列計為畢業學分或教育學程學分，並審慎考慮是否需申請停修，課程停修後，原申請畢業學分及教育學程學分之審核結果將作廢，請自行至教務處招生組或師資培育暨就業輔導中心辦理重新審核。</span></div> <div><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">      (</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt\">四) 申請停修後，請於第15週自行至學生資訊系統「線上查詢」、「歷年成績查詢」查詢本學期申請結果。</span></div>','公告101學年度第1學期學生申請停修課程事宜','','publish','open','open','','1011-sp-9770','','','2012-12-05 07:51:34','2012-12-04 23:51:34','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=591',31,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (692,1,'2012-12-10 03:57:15','2012-12-09 19:57:15','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">本系范丙林及蕭雅真老師指導學生詹騏謙、孫裴參加2012-4C數位創作競賽-動畫劇本組，以作品「顯微●鏡」榮獲大會頑石企業贊助獎!!<br /> <br /> 數位系/玩遊碩班 全體師生 敬賀</span></p>','【狂賀】本系大學部學生參加2012-4C數位創作競賽動畫劇本組榮獲頑石企業贊助獎','','publish','open','open','','2012-4c-2','','','2012-12-10 03:57:15','2012-12-09 19:57:15','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=592',32,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (693,1,'2012-12-10 04:27:12','2012-12-09 20:27:12','<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">國立臺北教育大學數位科技設計學系<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span></span></p> <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">公告</span></p> <p align=\"right\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:標楷體\">101</span><span style=\"font-family:標楷體\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>日</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:40.55pt;text-indent:-40.55pt;mso-char-indent-count:-3.12\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">主<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">    </span></span>旨：數位科技設計學系<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含玩具與遊戲設計碩士班<span lang=\"EN-US\">)101</span>學年度第一學期五年一貫學、碩士學位甄選申請審查結果。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:標楷體\"> </span></p> <p class=\"Default\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:標楷體\">依<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">    </span></span>據：</span><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">本系學生修讀五年一貫學、碩士學位甄選要點</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:標楷體\"> </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:42.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-42.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:-3.27;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">公告事項：</span></p> <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;mso-para-margin-left:0gd;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">一、<span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span>學年度第一學期共計有</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">何思頡<span lang=\"EN-US\">(109819007)</span>、林欣宜<span lang=\"EN-US\">(109919010)</span>、趙君晏<span lang=\"EN-US\">(110019007)</span>、蘇雅雯<span lang=\"EN-US\">(110019009)</span>及孫佩均<span lang=\"EN-US\">(110019037)</span>共五名同學申請。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.25pt;mso-para-margin-left:0gd;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體\">二、經本系<span lang=\"EN-US\">101</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>日五年一貫審查小組會議評選後，全數通過申請。</span></p> <span new=\"New\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:\">三、通過之學生自大三下學期<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>始得上修碩士班課程。</span>','101學年度第一學期五年一貫甄選結果公告','','publish','open','open','','101-sp-19062','','','2012-12-10 04:27:12','2012-12-09 20:27:12','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress3/?p=593',30,'post','',0);
